00:14:55.580 --> 00:14:58.910
♪Menjebakku di musim dingin ini♪

00:14:59.090 --> 00:15:02.460
♪Salju memenuhi kota,
melayang menuju cakrawala♪

00:15:02.710 --> 00:15:06.270
♪Membawa pergi kesedihan perpisahan♪

00:15:06.510 --> 00:15:10.100
♪Aku berlama-lama sendirian di salju♪

00:15:10.100 --> 00:15:14.330
♪Menunggu takdir
